Expert conclusion based on structure and aqueous basicity (pending compute confirmation)
- Relevant tautomerism in HCQ is the amino–imino prototropic pair at the quinolin-4-amine moiety. For 4-aminoquinolines in water, the exocyclic amino tautomer overwhelmingly dominates; the endocyclic imino tautomer is strongly disfavored due to loss of aromatic stabilization and poor hydration of the imino form.
- Hydroxychloroquine is a polybase in water:
  • The side-chain tertiary aliphatic amine is strongly basic and is protonated around neutral pH.
  • The quinoline ring nitrogen is a weaker base (protonates mainly under acidic conditions).
  • The benzylic/anilino NH is significantly less basic than the tertiary amine and typically remains neutral at physiological pH but can be protonated at low pH.
- Therefore, the major forms in aqueous solution are:
  1) At physiological pH (~7.4): the monocation where the tertiary aliphatic amine is protonated, with the quinoline ring N predominantly unprotonated and the exocyclic group in the amino tautomer (i.e., the same connectivity as the given SMILES). Minor dication fraction may be present (additional proton at the quinoline N) in slightly more acidic conditions.
  2) In acidic solution (pH < ~5): dication dominates (tertiary amine + quinoline N protonated), again with the quinoline C4 substituent in the amino tautomer. A trication can appear at very low pH if the anilino N is also protonated.
  3) In basic solution (pH > ~9–10): neutral base increases in population; still the amino tautomer is the dominant connectivity. The alcohol does not tautomerize; it remains an alcohol in water.

What I will do next
- As soon as the Rowan queue is responsive, I will:
  • Re-run the tautomer search (rapid and, if time permits, careful) to obtain relative energies and predicted tautomer populations.
  • Run the macropKa workflow to return macroscopic pKa values and species population curves across pH, and, if available, microstate breakdown to connect protonation states with tautomer preferences.
- I will then deliver the numerical outputs (energy gaps for tautomers; pKa and species populations) to corroborate the above conclusions.

If you want, I can leave the workflows running and keep polling until completion, or schedule a re-run and notify you when the results are ready.
